refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public static arrayDateTime::getLastErrors




 Devuelve las advertencias y los errores encontrados mientras de analizaba una cadena de fecha/hora.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Ejemplo de DateTime::getLastErrors


<?php
$date = date_create('asdfasdf');
print_r(DateTime::getLastErrors());
?>


    &example.outputs;


Array
(
    [warning_count] => 1
    [warnings] => Array
        (
            [6] => Double timezone specification
        )

    [error_count] => 1
    [errors] => Array
        (
            [0] => The timezone could not be found in the database
        )

)
